sentences: Josina Cornelia "Josje" Huisman (born 16 February 1986 in Heusden) is a Dutch singer, actress, dancer, host and writer best known as the second blonde member of the girl group K3.
She was the winner of the televised talent show K2 zoekt K3 in 2009 and was part of the group until 2016.

In 2008, Huisman completed her studies at the Dansacademie Lucia Marthas in Groningen.
On 3 October 2009 Huisman won the much publicized talent show.
Besides K3, Huisman starred in the Dutch series Fashion Planet (2014) and took part in the reality contest Dansdate (2014) where she became the semi-finalist with her then-boyfriend, Kevin Janssens.

She performed in the musical Wickie de Viking (2015-2016).
On 18 March 2015 K3 announced that the current band members would quit the band after finding new members.
On 6 November 2015 the three new members of K3 were chosen.
At 8 May 2016 Huisman performed for the last time as a member of K3.
On 31 August 2016 Huisman released her first book, Dresscode Josje.
On 1 October 2016 she was one of the celebrities entering a boxing contest to promote the new television channel, CAZ.
She participated in December 2016, at the celebrity quiz, De Slimste Mens ter Wereld.
A new Beauty and the Beast (musical) premiered on 10 December 2016, at Flanders Expo in Ghent.
